<p class="review-lesson">[91] Miracles are seen in light .</p>

<p><sup>2</sup> <em>I cannot see in darkness. Let the light</em><br /> Of holiness
and truth light up my mind,<br /> And let me see the innocence within.</p>

<p class="review-lesson">[92] Miracles are seen in light, and light and strength are one.</p>

<p><sup>3</sup> <em>I see through strength, the gift of God to me.</em><br /> My
weakness is the dark His gift dispels<br /> By giving me His strength to
take its place.</p>

